ZH: 我们需要一张磁卡才能打开这扇门。
EN: We need a magnetic card to open this door.

ZH: 这张磁卡是用来刷卡消费的。
EN: This magnetic card is used for swiping and making purchases.

ZH: 我的磁卡不见了，我得报失挂失。
EN: My magnetic card is lost, I need to report it and cancel it.

ZH: 他的磁卡可以存储大量的数据。
EN: His magnetic card can store a large amount of data.

ZH: 这个仪器只能使用磁卡进行读取。
EN: This device can only be read using a magnetic card.

ZH: 我们的公司设定了磁卡进入的权限。
EN: Our company has set permissions for access using magnetic cards.

ZH: 这家酒店的房间需要磁卡插卡才能通电。
EN: The rooms in this hotel require a magnetic card to insert in order to turn on the power.

ZH: 我们要换新的磁卡系统来提高安全性。
EN: We are upgrading to a new magnetic card system to enhance security.

ZH: 请用磁卡刷一下门口的感应器。
EN: Please swipe the magnetic card on the sensor at the entrance.

ZH: 他忘记了在公交车上看哪张磁卡。
EN: He forgot which magnetic card he used on the bus.

ZH: 新员工需要领取一张磁卡才能进入公司。
EN: New employees need to receive a magnetic card to access the company premises.

ZH: 我的磁卡过期了，需要去办理换新手续。
EN: My magnetic card has expired, I need to renew it.

ZH: 抱歉，您的磁卡无效，请联系客服处理。
EN: Sorry, your magnetic card is invalid, please contact customer service for assistance.

ZH: 为了安全起见，公司对磁卡进行了加密处理。
EN: For security reasons, the company has encrypted the magnetic cards.

ZH: 学生们需要用磁卡进入实验室。
EN: Students need to use a magnetic card to access the laboratory.

ZH: 他的磁卡被盗刷了大笔消费。
EN: His magnetic card was fraudulently used for large purchases.

ZH: 这家超市只接受特定品牌的磁卡支付。
EN: This supermarket only accepts payment using specific branded magnetic cards.

ZH: 该公司已经为员工自助餐厅实现了磁卡支付。
EN: The company has enabled magnetic card payment for the employee cafeteria.

ZH: 机器人需要一张磁卡来启动程序。
EN: The robot requires a magnetic card to start the program.

ZH: 请将磁卡插入读卡器，并按指示操作。
EN: Please insert the magnetic card into the card reader and follow the instructions.
